00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Oh, McCork, get away from me!

58
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,000
Places, everyone!

59
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:26,000
This just in from Rosalind. Is it true that love is blind?

60
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,000
Well, some studies have shown that love does suppress

61
