78
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:16,000
It's true, science can't explain everything

79
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,000
and we're still not entirely sure

80
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,000
why we really fall for the people we do.

81
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:24,000
